  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Ohio State University",
  "url": "https://www.osu.edu/",
  "description": "A large public land-grant research university in Columbus, Ohio, United States. Its public, programmatically accessible footprint includes University Libraries' Knowledge Bank DSpace 7.6 institutional repository (REST and OAI-PMH) and an institution-wide Shibboleth SAML 2.0 Single Sign-On service.",
